# Code Conventions: Bubblepi Store

## Naming

| Konteks           | Convention              | Contoh                          |
| ----------------- | ----------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Components        | PascalCase, named export| `ProductCard.tsx`               |
| Hooks             | use + PascalCase        | `useAuth.ts`                    |
| API routes        | kebab-case              | `/api/admin/orders`             |
| Server Actions    | verb + noun camelCase   | `createOrder`                   |
| DB tables         | PascalCase (Prisma)     | `OrderItem`                     |
| DB enums          | UPPER_SNAKE             | `PENDING_PAYMENT`               |
| Env vars          | UPPER_SNAKE             | `DATABASE_URL`                  |
| Lib functions     | camelCase               | `validateStock`                 |
| Lib modules       | kebab-case files        | `lib/suppliers/base.ts`         |
| Script files      | kebab-case              | `scripts/auto-cancel-expired-orders.ts` |
| Test files        | `*.test.ts` / `*.edge.test.ts` | `auth.test.ts`              |

## File Structure Rules

- **No barrel exports** — import langsung dari file
- **Co-locate related files** — `components/admin/AdminSidebar.tsx` bersama admin components
- **Server logic di `lib/`** — bukan di components
- **API handlers di `app/api/`** — ikuti App Router convention
- **Components pakai named export** — `export function Button()`
- **Server Actions pakai `'use server'` directive** — di atas file
- **Tidak import dari `dist/` atau `build/`**

## Import Order

```
1. React / Next.js imports
2. Third-party libraries (lucide-react, zod, etc.)
3. Internal: @/components, @/lib, @/hooks
4. Relative: ./local-file
```

## TypeScript Rules

- **Strict mode** — tidak ada `any`, tidak ada `@ts-ignore`
- **Gunakan Zod** untuk validation schemas
- **Prisma types** — gunakan `Prisma.XxxGetPayload<>` untuk complex queries
- **Avoid type assertions** — prefer type guards

## React / Next.js Rules

- **App Router only** — tidak ada Pages Router
- **Server Components by default** — `'use client'` hanya saat perlu interaktivitas
- **Server Actions** untuk mutations — export dengan `'use server'`
- **Dynamic imports** untuk heavy components (charts, editors)
- **Image optimization** — gunakan `next/image` dengan AVIF/WebP

## Styling Rules

- **Tailwind CSS v4** — gunakan utility classes
- **shadcn/ui components** — tidak ada UI library baru
- **CSS Variables** untuk theming (via shadcn)
- **Framer Motion** untuk animations
- **Responsive** — mobile-first approach

## Testing Rules

- **Framework:** node:test + node:assert
- **Edge tests:** `*.edge.test.ts` untuk edge cases
- **Mocking:** minimal mocking — prefer real integration tests
- **DB tests:** gunakan test database, bukan production

## Custom Conventions

- **Cron scripts** di `scripts/` — jalankan via `npx tsx scripts/[name].ts`
- **Cron API endpoints** di `app/api/cron/` — dipanggil oleh scheduler eksternal
- **Supplier system** modular di `lib/suppliers/` — extend via `base.ts`
- **Stock credentials** di-encrypt via AES-256 — jangan log plaintext
- **Order numbering** format: `BP-XXXXXXXX`